I"$	<CENTER><h1 class="emphnext">Things I Love</h1></CENTER>

<hr />

<p>They fill me with a sense of freedom and possibility and expansiveness. Or are associated with particular places and phases of my life. The things we love can reveal our inner selves in a way that personal biographies or self-descriptions cannot.</p>

<hr />

