 the night sky, photos of earth from space, Jurgen Klopp, Cate Blanchett, <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dE1DuBesGYM">this ted talk by Jane McGonigall</a>, <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2006/08/20/sports/playmagazine/20federer.html?pagewanted=all">this essay on Roger Federer by David Foster Wallace</a>, the music of Bach, Wodehouse, Courtney Barnett, Raghuram Rajan, <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pdcy4fbLwuc&amp;list=PLdIS7dENF-nWYmcIjtKQjCvqthfjse1iw&amp;index=4">this tribute video of IIT Delhi</a>, Chandigarh, Andy Murray, Liverpool vs AC Milan Champions League Final 2005, Liverpool vs Barcelona Champions League Semi-Final 2019 , Wimbledon, Nadal vs Federer 2008 Wimbledon Final, IIT Delhi, Mathematics, Nietzscheâ€™s Philosophy, Barbican Hall, British Library, IHC,  Sector 6 Panchkula ,</p>

